Zip Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 07/25/23

Zes ("we," "our," or "us") values your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data when you use Zip (referred to as "the Bot") created by Zes. By using the Bot, you consent to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect:
a. Discord User Data: When you add the Bot to your Discord server and use its services, we may collect certain user data, including Discord user IDs, server IDs, message content, and file attachments.
b. Usage Data: We may collect non-personal information about how you interact with the Bot, such as commands used, response times, and error logs. This data helps us improve the Bot's performance and functionality.

c. Cookies and Similar Technologies: We do not use cookies or similar tracking technologies to collect information.

How We Use Your Information:
a. Providing Bot Services: We use the collected data to provide the requested services and features of the Bot, including file editing using FFmpeg and other APIs.
b. Improving the Bot: Usage data helps us understand how users interact with the Bot, enabling us to identify and address performance issues and enhance user experience.

c. Data Security: We may use your data to monitor and ensure the security of the Bot, including investigating and preventing unauthorized access or usage.

Data Sharing and Disclosure:
a. Third-Party Service Providers: We may share your data with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the Bot and providing its services. These providers have limited access to your data and are obligated to protect it in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
b. Legal Requirements: We may disclose your data if required to do so by law or in response to valid legal requests from law enforcement authorities or other government agencies.

c. Business Transfers: In the event of a merger, acquisition, or any form of asset sale, your data may be transferred as part of the transaction. We will notify you of such an occurrence and your choices regarding your data.

Data Retention:
We will retain your data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.

Data Security:
We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of data transmission or storage can be entirely secure. Therefore, while we strive to protect your data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Children's Privacy:
The Bot is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have unintentionally collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately, and we will take appropriate steps to remove the data from our records.

Changes to this Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any modifications will be effective immediately upon posting the revised Privacy Policy on the official website or through the Discord server where the Bot is hosted. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to this Privacy Policy, please contact us at https://discord.gg/QtYFetctVT.

By using the Bot, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to the collection, use, and disclosure of your data as described herein.

Zes
Zip Creator

